### Stack
- React 19 + TypeScript, Vite
- **XState v5** + `@xstate/react` — all business and page logic in state machines
- **React Router v6** — URL routing (nested routes, `<Outlet>`)
- **Recharts** — `AreaChart` (Document Activity), `PieChart` (Country Distribution)
- **Sass** — component-scoped `.scss` per BEM convention
- IBM Plex Sans — loaded via Google Fonts in `index.html`

