### Routing
| Path          | Component  | Notes                              |
|---------------|------------|------------------------------------|
| `/`           | redirect   | → /dashboard                       |
| `/dashboard`  | Dashboard  | Overview, stats, charts            |
| `/invoices`   | Invoices   | Document list (stub)               |
| `/customers`  | Customers  | Customer management (stub)         |
| `/analytics`  | Analytics  | Deep analytics (stub)              |
| `/settings`   | Settings   | Account/platform settings (stub)   |
| `/users`      | Users      | User management panel (stub)       |
| `/*`          | redirect   | → /dashboard                       |

Navigation flows: user clicks Navbar → `send({ type: 'NAVIGATE', route })` → homeMachine transitions state → `useEffect` calls `navigate('/${route}')` → React Router renders matching `<Route>`.

