### Machine Hierarchy
```
App machine (auth gateway)
  └─ Home machine (data loading + routing)
       ├─ Dashboard machine (stats + charts)
       ├─ Invoices machine (stub)
       ├─ Customers machine (stub)
       ├─ Analytics machine (stub)
       ├─ Settings machine (stub)
       └─ Users machine (stub)
```
The App machine controls WHEN Home is rendered. Each page machine is independent and only runs while its route is active.

