### API Reference
Base URL: `https://documents-web-services.onrender.com`
Local Base URL: `http://localhost:8000` (configured in `src/constants/urls.ts`)
Auth: session cookie (`credentials: 'include'`). API key also available in user profile.

| Endpoint                        | Method | Used In         | Response Key                    |
|---------------------------------|--------|-----------------|---------------------------------|
| `/auth/me`                      | GET    | Home actors     | `data` → UserProfile            |
| `/api/country-settings/public`  | GET    | Home actors     | `data.countries` → Country[]    |
| `/api/customers`                | GET    | Customer actors | `data` → Customer[]             |
| `/api/customers`                | POST   | Customer actors | `data` → Customer               |
| `/api/invoices`                 | GET    | Invoice actors  | `data` → Invoice[]              |
| `/api/invoices`                 | POST   | Invoice actors  | `data` → Invoice                |

