### Theme System
- `html.dark` / `html.light` classes applied before React renders (script in `index.html`)
- CSS variables defined in `src/index.css` under `html.dark { }` and `html.light { }`
- Portal routes → saved theme from `localStorage('crimson:theme')`, default: light
- Public routes (`/`, `/login`, `/home`) → always light
- Key variables: `--color-bg`, `--color-card`, `--color-surface`, `--color-border`, `--color-text-primary`, `--color-text-secondary`, `--color-accent` (#e53e3e red), `--color-success` (#48bb78), `--color-warning` (#ecc94b)

