### Implemented Pages & Features

#### Theme Toggle (Navbar)
- Navbar now has its own machine (`src/components/Navbar/machine/`) managing `dropdownOpen` and `theme` state.
- Clicking the user icon opens a dropdown with: user name/email, Light/Dark Mode toggle, Sign Out button.
- Theme toggle updates `document.documentElement.className` and saves to `localStorage('crimson:theme')`.
- Navbar receives `user: UserProfile | null` prop from Home.tsx; `onSignOut` is optional.
- Machine pattern: inline `assign` in `machine.ts` (avoids XState v5 type inference issues with external `assign` functions).

#### Invoices Page (`src/pages/Invoices/`)
- Full implementation: status tabs (All/Pending/Accepted/Rejected), country selector, search input, document table.
- Machine: loading → loaded | error; events: REFRESH, SELECT_COUNTRY, SELECT_STATUS, SEARCH.
- Filtering is client-side (from context).
- Country column added to table with badge display.
- Status badges: green (accepted), red (rejected), yellow (pending).

#### Customers Page (`src/pages/Customers/`)
- Two-panel layout: left sidebar (country filter with emoji flags + counts), right panel (table + search).
- Machine: loading → loaded | error; events: REFRESH, SELECT_COUNTRY, SEARCH.
- Customer data from `customers.txt` (9 customers across AO, NG, PT, SA).
- Country flags via `COUNTRY_FLAGS` map (code → emoji).
- Table: CUSTOMER ID, TAX ID, NAME, EMAIL, PHONE, COUNTRY (flag + name + code), ACTIONS (edit/delete icons).
- Header buttons: Download, Upload, Add Customer.

#### Analytics Page (`src/pages/Analytics/`)
- KPI cards: Total Documents, Acceptance Rate, Rejection Rate, Active Countries.
- Monthly trends: recharts `AreaChart` with multi-country overlaid areas (AO/NG/PT/SA).
- Doc type breakdown: recharts `PieChart`.
- Country comparison: recharts `BarChart` (accepted/rejected/pending per country).
- Country stats table with acceptance rate bar.
- Machine: loading → loaded | error; event: REFRESH.

#### Settings Page (`src/pages/Settings/`)
- Two-column layout matching design:
  - Left: Profile Information (name, NIF, email, address fields, brand image uploader, Save Profile).
  - Right: Invoice Terms (with edit toggle), Change Password, API Credentials (show/copy/generate), Auto Submit toggle.
- Bottom: Purge Invoice Workspace danger zone.
- Local React state for form values and UI toggles (autoSubmit, showApiKey, editingTerms).
- Machine: loading → loaded | error; events: REFRESH, SAVE.

